OL,3,CRayner announces drastic reforms to
OL,4,Chouse planning rules to build 1.5m
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FThe Deputy Prime Minister has re-
OL,8,Fintroduced new mandatory building
OL,9,Ftargets among other measures to help
OL,10,Fspeed up the building of new homes, as
OL,11,FITV News political correspondent Carl
OL,12,FDinnen reports.
OL,14,FAngela Rayner has announced an
OL,15,Foverhaul of the planning system, with
OL,16,Fmandatory housing targets re-
OL,17,Fintroduced to pave the way for 1.5
OL,18,Fmillion new homes over the next five
OL,19,Fyears.
