OL,3,CRayner announces drastic reforms to
OL,4,Chouse planning rules to build 1.5m
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FThe deputy prime minister and housing
OL,8,Fsecretary has reversed a decision made
OL,9,Fby the Conservative government to
OL,10,Fscrap housing targets, which will free
OL,11,Fup some green belt land for
OL,12,Fconstruction.
OL,14,F"What I say won't be without
OL,15,Fcontroversy, but this is urgent
OL,16,Fbecause this Labour government is not
OL,17,Fafraid to take on the tough choices
OL,18,Fneeded to deliver for our country",
OL,19,FRayner told MPs in the House of
OL,20,FCommons on Tuesday.
