OL,3,CRayner announces drastic reforms to
OL,4,Chouse planning rules to build 1.5m
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FHer reforms make explicit that the
OL,8,Fdefault answer to brownfield
OL,9,Fdevelopment should be "yes" and
OL,10,Fpromote homebuilding at greater
OL,11,Fdensities in urban centres, like towns
OL,12,Fand cities.
OL,14,FBut because there is not enough
OL,15,Fbrownfield land in the country to meet
OL,16,Fhousing needs, the government will
OL,17,Fallow the targeted release of so-
OL,18,Fcalled grey belt land, which includes
OL,19,Fdisused petrol stations and car parks
OL,20,Fon parts of protected land known as
OL,21,Fthe green belt.
