OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,F"This is urgent", Rayner tells Commons
OL,9,FAny green belt land released will be
OL,10,Fsubject to "golden rules" to ensure
OL,11,Fthe development delivers 50%
OL,12,Faffordable homes and has access to
OL,13,Fgreen spaces and infrastructure such
OL,14,Fas schools and GP surgeries.
OL,16,FThe method for local authorities to
OL,17,Fcalculate how much land they must
OL,18,Fallocate for new housing, which relied
OL,19,Fon data from 2014, will be updated to
OL,20,Fensure stock is boosted in every part
OL,21,Fof the country.
