OL,4,Chouse planning rules to build 1.5m
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FRayner also unveiled immediate
OL,8,Fmeasures to counter the decline in the
OL,9,Fnumber of social and affordable
OL,10,Fhousing through new flexibilities for
OL,11,Fcouncils, including allowing them to
OL,12,Fuse their right-to-buy receipts to
OL,13,Fbuild and buy more social homes.
OL,15,F"Today I'm calling on local
OL,16,Fauthorities, housing associations and
OL,17,Findustry to work with me to deliver a
OL,18,Fcouncil house revolution," Ms Rayner
OL,19,Ftold the Commons, promising the
OL,20,F"biggest boost to social and
OL,21,Faffordable housing in a generation".
