OL,4,Chouse planning rules to build 1.5m
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FLabour also intends to drop the
OL,8,Frequirement for new homes to be
OL,9,F"beautiful", introduced by the
OL,10,FConservatives, arguing it is
OL,11,Fsubjective, difficult to define and
OL,12,Fleads to inconsistent decision-making
OL,13,Fon applications.
OL,15,FThe ruling party's manifesto used
OL,16,Fdifferent language, outlining instead
OL,17,Fits aim for "exemplary" development to
OL,18,Fbe "the norm not the exception".
