OL,7,FVarious new Cabinet ministers have
OL,8,Faddressed the Commons over the last
OL,9,Fweek to outline the issues they have
OL,10,Ffound in their departments since
OL,11,Ftaking over, blaming the former Tory
OL,12,Fgovernment for mismanagement.
OL,14,FOn Monday Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,15,Fsaid there is a #22 billion hole in
OL,16,Fthe public finances, blaming the
OL,17,Fformer government for overspending on
OL,18,Fthis year's budgets by billions of
OL,19,Fpounds after making a series of
OL,20,F"unfunded commitments".
